        public void deleteID(String uniqueId)
        Description copied from class: AbstractDatabaseHandler
        Attempts to delete the object with the uniqueId. If the object does not exist, it will fail silently. Use AbstractDatabaseHandler.objectExists(String) if you need to know if the object is in the database beforehand.
